  The return value is as follows:

  \begin{tabular}{r@@{\hs}l}
  \textbf{0}  & The pause was not cancelled. \\
  \textbf{1}  & The pause was cancelled with a left click. \\
  \textbf{-1} & The pause was cancelled with a right click. \\
  \end{tabular}
@}

